    {
      "id": "views-authoring-step-4",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Step 4",
      "position": {
        "x": 100,
        "y": -660
      },
      "width": 480,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-surface-authoring-walkthrough"
        },
        "markdown": "## Step 4: Consume The Declared Surface\n\nIn a separate consumer graph:\n- target the demo graph\n- choose `consume` or another appropriate behavior\n- select one of the declared surfaces\n\nThe important rule is simple:\n**the target graph tells the consumer what surfaces exist**"
      }
    },
